abstracts.cdata!:
The Technical Assistance Project will
            finance technical assistance in pre-investment planning,
            feasibility and engineering studies, consulting and advisory
            services and training for staff of agencies responsible for
            project planning or implementation. Emphasis would be on
            agriculture and water development sectors.
